{"tid":2053394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美制裁33間中國企業6月5日生效","createTime":"2020-06-06T09:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T14:07:17.000Z","uid":25468,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc2ce588986f48cd8468ba75006e997a1e02fa8","tid":2053394,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"美國商務部將於6月5日開始正式對33間列入貿易黑名單的中國企業或機構實施經濟制裁。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部上月公布，將33間中國政府機構及中資企業納入經濟制裁黑名單，其中24間中國政府組織及商業實體，涉及參與中國軍方的採購活動，危及美國國家安全，有9間中國企業及機構遭到制裁，涉及協助中國政府侵犯新疆維吾爾族人權。<br />\n<br />\n遭列入黑名單的公司，包括中國網絡安全公司奇虎360、從事人臉識別業務的人工智能公司東方網力等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2486327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F2486327&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=3459b806\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2486327</a>"},{"pid":"6c5cd279ca3a80e7b17ee21af7067cb131561f5c","tid":2053394,"uid":104034,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:07:13.000Z","msg":"Old news"},{"pid":"25921e6eb7b4fd190c69100a6391b4c305837295","tid":2053394,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"今日生效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bece4a8f9ea6091b4b2a9e11390c54f9293201","tid":2053394,"uid":25468,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6c5cd279ca3a80e7b17ee21af7067cb131561f5c","tid":2053394,"uid":104034,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:07:13.000Z","msg":"Old news"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:08:21.000Z","msg":"啱啱生效左 5 個鐘啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90d0fe7aedb5922e51c36716d5f1985cd6f75d4","tid":2053394,"uid":104034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4bece4a8f9ea6091b4b2a9e11390c54f9293201","tid":2053394,"uid":25468,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6c5cd279ca3a80e7b17ee21af7067cb131561f5c","tid":2053394,"uid":104034,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:07:13.000Z","msg":"Old news"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:08:21.000Z","msg":"啱啱生效左 5 個鐘啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但一早公佈左"},{"pid":"e9e44fd2f3a94ef0a75e2177d74a2f914149b4b5","tid":2053394,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"一通過國安法,美國做野快到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8336ef592b821892111c3886b705dadf863a3a","tid":2053394,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:14:48.000Z","msg":"這些企業及部門被列入貿易黑名單後，華府即可根據《出口管理條例》，限制對涉事機構出口、進口或轉口，意味它們無法和美國進行任何商業交易。"},{"pid":"bb2624386735145a9fcbb614ad851118b49434d3","tid":2053394,"uid":126305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"國安法比美國更大藉口制裁同速度"},{"pid":"d5619652c5670040a25dc5fa6a0d924d25e9e928","tid":2053394,"uid":6594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"幾時到HIKVISION"},{"pid":"c90535d1fe75c2d073667c2f7617fc433c6d034d","tid":2053394,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:43:10.000Z","msg":"衞士360 呢？"},{"pid":"8459a2742978f0872969d292465c8572acb7b442","tid":2053394,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:43:42.000Z","msg":"奇虎360<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91201ee07382b55601196dd194fcffe9e61cc0d","tid":2053394,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d5619652c5670040a25dc5fa6a0d924d25e9e928","tid":2053394,"uid":6594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"幾時到HIKVISION"